                                    "aonid": 221
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "Ysoki Snares",
                        "type": "section",
                        "text": "Although not so fond of them as kobolds, it's common for ratfolk to use snares and traps to defend their warrens. The placement and triggers for permanent traps are carefully considered to avoid wandering ysoki, especially children. Snares or even simple caltrops are often preferred as an alternative, deployed when the warren is threatened.",
                        "sources": [
                            {
                                "type": "source",
                                "name": "Monster Core",
                                "link": {
